    div.item-body
      div#interactive-content
        p Slide the control from side-to-side to fade between the three images: a "blue/black" version where we subtract out the theoretical color of the light (#524922), the original picture, and a "white/gold" version where we add color to compensate for the perceived shadow (#392c00).
        span Blue/Black 
            input(type="range" id="range" min="0" max="100" value="50")
            | White/Gold 
            button(id="reset") Reset

        div(class="container")
        img(id="a" src="/assets/a.jpg?1")
        img(id="b" src="/assets/b.jpg?1")
        img(id="c" src="/assets/c.jpg?1")

